Start
    Input number of frames
    Input reference string
    page_faults = 0
    For each page in reference string:
        If page not in frames:
            If frames not full:
                Add page
            Else:
                For each page in frame:
                    Find the page that will not be used for longest time
                Replace that page
            Increment page_faults
    Display total page faults
Stop

